      "writtenOn": "2026-06-30T16:27:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "CreateUser2 does not support UserPasswordExpired as a UserProperty in the D-Bus interface only UserPrivilege, UserGroups, UserEnabled, and PasswordExpiration are supported.\nhttps://github.com/openbmc/phosphor-dbus-interfaces/blob/master/yaml/xyz/openbmc_project/User/Manager.interface.yaml",
